      "updated": 1741664233723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- OpenAI GPT-2 (2019): 1.6 billion parameters trained on 100 billion tokens\n- Llama 3 (2024): 405 billion parameters trained on 15 trillion tokens\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- OpenAI GPT-2 (2019): 1.6 billion parameters trained on 100 billion tokens\n- Llama 3 (2024): 405 billion parameters trained on 15 trillion tokens\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "_KkgVLaTPHxIwQWTukFCd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3062.128956094262,
      "y": 1008.305044898548,
      "width": 734.1888573308506,
      "height": 81,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
