      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 633553520,
      "version": 940,
      "versionNonce": 435862128,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1741698267345,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GPT-2 是OpenAI于2019年公布的模型\n论文: \"Language Models are Unsupervised Multitask Learners\"\n\nTransformer 神经网络用了:\n- 16亿参数\n- 最大上下文长度 1024个token\n- 模型在1000亿 tokens长度的知识基础上训练的\n\nMy reproduction with llm.c:\nhttps://github.com/karpathy/llm.c/discussions/677\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GPT-2 是OpenAI于2019年公布的模型\n论文: \"Language Models are Unsupervised Multitask Learners\"\n\nTransformer 神经网络用了:\n- 16亿参数\n- 最大上下文长度 1024个token\n- 模型在1000亿 tokens长度的知识基础上训练的\n\nMy reproduction with llm.c:\nhttps://github.com/karpathy/llm.c/discussions/677\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
